{"tid":2515354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共政府公開宣佈「文革發動」？","createTime":"2021-05-04T02:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T04:25:55.000Z","uid":101392,"like":160,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"814d8e5f5fb86aa0784bbe4ce9ae49eace4ecbd0","tid":2515354,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSffqtxm1HzsfQCMY6yotMSJtWjQHiLtGSWNJgZFTpRpo?filename=PQqcoYF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQqcoYF.jpg&h=c19fcfa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（「廣播處」處長李百全、「民政事務局」局長徐英偉、前「特首」夫人梁唐青儀）<br />\n<br />\nSource: 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4131438200275102/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F4131438200275102%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=a067a0d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4131438200275102/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【港台五四升旗　李百全未回應刪 YouTube、不續約利君雅】<br />\n<br />\n/三人戴印有「世紀長征」字樣的紫色口罩，身後則有「文革發動」、「澳門回歸」、「世紀長征」等直幡。<br />\n<br />\n/宣言內容包含「愛祖國」、「心繫家國」、「民族共融」、「振興中華」等字眼，卻隻字不提五四運動中廣為提倡的「民主」和「科學」。<br />\n<br />\n/梁唐青儀見記者時表示，將有 100 集有關近代中國歷史紀錄片在港台電視31台播出，當中將包括六四事件及文化大革命。被問到會否擔心節目上載網上一段時間後會被下架，梁唐青儀則表示暫未與港台商討會否將節目上載至 YouTube。/"},{"pid":"a59450c35998b58555f270f6924002ffe0b6c83e","tid":2515354,"uid":151074,"like":122,"dislike":1,"score":121,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:34:28.000Z","msg":"文革發動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宜家比較少咁樣講到岀面嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c8f0f019d6f794ce41af97158edfb2dab95b11",