es/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部地主有樓人土都要捉去勞動改造洗廁所? <br />\n物業就拎出黎送俾無產階級住?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737e8c93d0ee894ceb2a82cbae2a67e135678877","tid":2515354,"uid":124455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:22:56.000Z","msg":"今次真係夠痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d483c03f40050dc896b3bb89e824ff22f4d2579f","tid":2515354,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8d76069b049d23fb432f5823bc8cdfd1a768355","tid":2515354,"uid":101392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fed077b2f74c44a4edf2e1b302c9a2b76ee9c346","tid":2515354,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e0d9debeffde3206fb075eec70739334ed55926","tid":2515354,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:44:41.000Z","msg":"後面白衫嗰件係咩制服 成個水手咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:45:49.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪港版紅衛兵<br />\n「香港少年軍」"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:47:00.000Z","msg":"/由前特首梁振英、前中聯辦主任張曉明任榮譽贊助人的香港青少年軍總會於前年初成立，是香港唯一以中式軍事步操為訓練基礎的制服團體。<br />\n香港青少年軍總會大樓今日（3日）開放予傳媒參觀，並即場示範多個訓練項目；現場教官及團員間的口令均以國語對答，<span class=\"red\">解放軍訓練拳軍體拳更是必修科，訓練期間一眾青少年會喊「殺」、「打」助威，解放軍駐港部隊亦會親授教官國家基本知識</span>。/<br />\n<br />\nsource: hk01"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />紅衛兵？"},{"pid":"2aaf2746411c2dbb69f304acc86189f6d5ff531b","tid":2515354,"uid":373900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"814d8e5f5fb86aa0784bbe4ce9ae49eace4ecbd0","tid":2515354,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQqcoYF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQqcoYF.jpg&h=c19fcfa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（「廣播處」處長李百全、「民政事務局」局長徐英偉、前「特首」夫人梁唐青儀）<br />\n<br />\nSource: 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4131438200275102/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F4131438200275102%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=a067a0d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4131438200275102/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【港台五四升旗　李百全未回應刪 YouTube、不續約利君雅】<br />\n<br />\n/三人戴印有「世紀長征」字樣的紫色口罩，身後則有「文革發動」、「澳門回歸」、「世紀長征」等直幡。<br />\n<br />\n/宣言內容包含「愛祖國」、「心繫家國」、「民族共融」、「振興中華」等字眼，卻隻字不提五四運動中廣為提倡的「民主」和「科學」。<br />\n<br />\n/梁唐青儀見記者時表示，將有 100 集有關近代中國歷史紀錄片在港台電視31台播出，當中將包括六四事件及文化大革命。被問到會否擔心節目上載網上一段時間後會被下架，梁唐青儀則表示暫未與港台商討會否將節目上載至 YouTube。/"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:24:10.000Z","msg":"文革係咪要炮打司令部? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而加要全香港人組織紅衛兵出黎批鬥高官? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府高層囝囡係咪要全部捉去新界耕田,上山下鄉?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警務人員、全體公務員要學雷鋒, 要全心服務人民, 全部唔準有工資?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打倒階級敵人, 有多過一層樓就全家黑五類, 全家跪玻璃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部地主有樓人土都要捉去勞動改造洗廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n物業就拎出黎送俾無產階級住?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4846a4ac6d2a2082ac0f66b1c51197d9b48b155","tid":2515354,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:26:38.000Z","msg":"而家真係無底線"},{"pid":"b68f6f8bf5c1f541d12707124beb4be6d38e1901","tid":2515354,"uid":209398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:26:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=420398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=